{
  "texts": [
    "Lameli and Schönberg [2023] present a measure for spatial language variation.",
    "Using distance between locations as a heuristic for dialectal similarity, they examine variations in dialects of German.",
    "Also, Keleg et al. [2023] use a dataset in Arabic labeled with the degree of dialectness, to train a BERT-based regression model.",
    "Ethical & Social ImplicationsOverall, dialectal NLP presents an excellent avenue for research with huge social implications.",
    "We highlight three considerations of relevance."
  ]
}